longBusinessSummary: Diamond Estates Wines & Spirits Inc. produces, markets, and sells wines in Canada, China, and internationally. The company operates in two segments, Manufactured Wines and Agency. It produces vintner quality alliance and blended wines under the 20 Bees, EastDell, Lakeview Cellars, Dan Aykroyd, Fresh, McMichael Collection, Seasons, Serenity, and Backyard Vineyards brand names. The company also acts as a sales agent for approximately 120 beverage alcohol brands. It sells its products through liquor boards, licensed restaurants and bars, and grocery chains; and its two retail locations, as well as online. The company is based in Niagara-on-the-Lake, Canada.
